import { Typography, Label, Input } from "@mui/material"
import FormControlUnstyled from '@mui/base/FormControlUnstyled';
import { Box } from "@mui/system"
import Log from '../assets/background/back.svg'

const Login = () => {

    return(
        <Box>
            <Box component='img' src={Log} position='absolute'/>
            <Box position='relative'>
                <Box sx={{
                    position: 'absolute',
                    top: '50%',
                    left: '50%',
                    background: 'white'
                }}>
                    <Typography>Sign In</Typography>
                    <Typography width='65%'>Please sign up to your personal account if you want to use all our premium products</Typography>
                    <FormControlUnstyled defaultValue="" required>
                    <Label>Name</Label>
                    <Input />
                    </FormControlUnstyled>
                </Box>
            </Box>
        </Box>
    )
}

export default Login
